        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed order-1 md:order-2">ALO has focused on implementing programs that promote the Right to Livelihood and the Right to Health for vulnerable and marginalized populations, particularly indigenous and economically disadvantaged communities. Guided by a dedicated team of young volunteers, the organization has:
•	Collaborated with public and private legal aid institutions to provide free legal assistance and prevent human rights violations.
•	Promoted social justice, sustainable livelihoods, education, and health awareness in -erserved communities.
